Package Commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cmd
    This class implements commands to be used from the console and that affect the World.
    CmdParser
    Parses a string into its corresponding command
    Create
    Creates a SimpleCell in the specified position
    Destroy
    Destroys the Cell/Virus in the specified position
    EasterEgg
    ???
    Exit
    Exits the program
    Help
    Prints the help string of each command.
    Load
    Loads a World from a plain text file.
    MeteorFall
    Kills every Cell and Virus in the World.
    PlayComplex
    Creates a new simulation with both Cells and Virus.
    PlaySimple
    Creates a new simulation with only SimpleCells.
    Save
    Saves the current game state to a plain text file.
    Step
    Executes one step of the simulation.
